text: Sanzhar Mussayev is a Kazakhstani archer. He was born on 11 April 1996. Mussayev competed at the 2020 Summer Olympics.Sanzhar MusayevSanzhar MUSSAYEV == References == Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani archers Category:Olympians for Kazakhstan
